<br>
Is there some formula for calculating max damage per level? <br>
<br>
Do different pets hit for different max damage? <br>
<br>
Do they all get the same damage when wielding a weapon? <br>
<br>
I expected to find that kind of information in the FAQ, but its not there. Can anyone answer these questions and then add them to the FAQ?<br>
<br>
Also, the link states that pets will take 50% of exp if they do half or more of damage. I believe that changed a few patches ago, yes?<br>
